### GET /api/v1/llm/backends/{backendId}/variants
### Returns the list of {release_id, platform, accelerator_profile} combos
### available for this machine, with a recommended marker.

GET {{host}}/api/v1/llm/backends/llama.cpp/variants HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json

### 200 OK — happy path
###
### {
###   "meta": { "timestamp": "2026-04-17T12:00:00Z" },
###   "data": {
###     "recommended_release_id": "b6859",
