### 404 NOT_FOUND — unknown backend id
###
### { "meta": {...}, "error": { "code": "not_found", "message": "backend foo not found" } }

### 404 CATALOG_UNAVAILABLE — version manifest missing / malformed (Q1-edge3)
###
### { "meta": {...}, "error": { "code": "catalog_unavailable", "message": "version manifest not found on disk" } }
